Absolutely beautiful icons which would look great with the supplied wallpapers... BUT the oversized wallpapers do not scale-down to fit a tablet screen, so only a small portion of the aesthetically balanced wallpaper appears on the screen. The icons work nicely in Nova launcher and especially in Launcher++ which complements their snappy squareness. Unfortunately there are far too few icons to choose from at the moment. Many of your favourite apps are not catered for, and suitable replacement icons are scarce. For example, there is very little in the Cleaner or Chromecasting line. This problem is heightened when it comes to folders. One of Nova's best features (and Launcher++ too) is putting app icons together in a folder. However this icon pack has just 1 folder icon, unembellished, and too few thematic icons to make up the shortfall.
